gen (mumps skin test antigen)." Aventis Pharmaceuticals, Swiftwater, PA.[5] "Product Information. Multitest CMI (skin test antigens, multiple)." Aventis Pharmaceuticals, Swiftwater, PA.[6] "Product Information. Histolyn-Cyl (histoplasmin)." ALK Laboratories Inc, Wallingford, CT.', 1767369485);
